{"title":"渤滩的红荆","authors":["刘小放"],"dates":[{"year":1986,"month":11,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"渤滩的红荆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘小放"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从旋风里落下一粒种子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落在祖父跋涉的脚印里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个坚韧的灵魂复活了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从凝固的苦涩里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爆出扭动的寒光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命之根"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照亮沉积的岁月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早春"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"豁然抽出一柄红剑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刺破荒滩千秋空茫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一炷跳跃的火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燃起篷篷绿焰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼唤着风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼唤着小鸟和蓝天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条金色的火狐之尾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一缕鲜活的灵气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘摇在寥廓的天地间"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}